Description: Diaperpedia is a community app for parents, helping them locate baby changing tables.
Headquarters Regions: San Francisco Bay Area, West Coast, Western US
Full Description: Available for the iPhone, iPod and iPad, Diaperpedia allows users to find, add, edit, and review diaper changing locations so parents like them can feel a little surer the next time they're away from home. It’s free to download, and because we know you’ll have your hands full, we want to make it worth your while.  Find: You have an unlimited amount of choices but not all of them have changing tables. Let Diaperpedia help narrow it down for you. Add: Local Grocery store. Check. Favorite Restaurant. Check. Corner Coffee shop. Check. You’re there anyway, make it worth a chance to win Diaperpedia’s gift card contest. Use your device to easily input the location detail when you see a baby changing table or Diaper deck. That simple. Edit: Whoops! Did the restaurant take out the table in a remodel? Flag the location. Dads, did they add a Men’s room changing table? Edit the location quickly to reflect that. Daddy’s turn!  Review: Baby Changing tables are not all the same. Some are more accessible or in better condition. Perhaps you’ve discovered the Rolls-Royce of baby changing tables or one you don’t care to visit again. Take a picture, and review it so you’ll remember it the next time you’re out and about. Contest*: You are automatically entered to win Diaperpedia’s monthly gift card contest for every qualified location you add. Add the location detail directly into your Diaperpedia app using the drop pin method (our favorite), or the add location buttons throughout the app. You can win the $50 card for the most locations, or be one of two randomly selected entrants for $25 each. Use the gift card for diapers, wipes, or whatever you need to make being a parent a little easier. So, the next time you’re out with your baby, please consider taking Diaperpedia, and the collective insight of parents just like you, with you.

Headquarters Regions: San Francisco Bay Area, West Coast, Western US
Full Description: Alite Designs Inc. is a small group of rabblerousers that wants you to go outside more! Since their home base is San Francisco they know first hand that city living is a lame excuse for being cooped up. Magical outdoor fun is all around thems, no matter the location. They make a bunch of cool stuff that helps you get out there!  Alite Designs outdoor gear can be found in any fine outdoor retailer nationwide. (Here’s a list!) If you’re not near any of these retailers, you can always pick up any Alite products online in the Alite web store. AND, if you are a Bay Area native, then we highly encourage you to visit the Alite Outpost, our local retail storefront, on Fridays from 12-6pm, located at 2505 Mariposa Street. If you are brand new to the world of camping and outdoor, then come talk to us about your upcoming outdoor excursion ideas, figure out the proper gear for your next trip, and ask about good places to go as you venture into the fresh air!  Alite Designs is all about well-designed products that are extremely functional and ridiculously fun and easy to use. Their award-winning Monarch chair weighs a mere pound, collapses to the size of super burrito for easy travel, and can sit on almost any terrain (level or not). Their Sexy Hotness sleeping bags let you walk around, use the outdoor lavatory, and zip up with other fellow (or fella) Sexy Hotness sleeping bag inhabitants to make room for two! Hell, you can zip as many bags together as you like… they don’t judge. Their outdoor cooking utensil, the Clover Cook set, includes both a stirring spoon and spatula that combine to form tongs! This utensil nails all of your cooking needs in one handy set of utensils that nest together for easy organization and portability. All products from Alite are designed to get you excited about going outside!  Alite Designs is very much about promoting their wonderful Bay Area community! They make a point to work with local, like-minded makers and organizations to produce amazing collaborative products, promote fun events, and raise money for causes that are close to them. They also practice ethical, sustainable manufacturing processes and produce special product lines exclusively here in San Francisco.

Headquarters Regions: San Francisco Bay Area, Silicon Valley, West Coast
Full Description: TAL Global is an international security consulting and risk management firm that provides a comprehensive array of investigative, disaster mitigation planning and risk management services. Our extensive international network of professionals enables us to provide our clients with the highest level of security and loss prevention services around the globe. Our commitment to an impeccable standard of ethics has earned us an unparalleled international reputation for professionalism and excellence among many Fortune 500 corporations. Catastrophic incidents, whether natural or manmade, are rarely predictable, but the better the advance preparation for crisis, the more likely a situation can be mitigated, yielding a more positive outcome. In fact, emergency preparedness is often the critical factor that determines long-term survival of organizations in the face of the unexpected. TAL Global recognizes the integral value of security and crisis management within business and governmental planning processes. We understand the negative impact a disaster can have on the bottom line. We work together with our clients to provide assessment, planning, management and training that enable them to weather any storm – real or figurative. Businesses and governmental agencies must also be prepared to deal with the ever-changing methods for theft of intellectual and real property and the growing challenges of securing tangible assets and information. TAL Global employs state-of-the-art assessment and investigative tools to help our clients optimize their access and protection strategies. We support and complement existing internal security operations, providing the needed expertise to diffuse and eliminate predatory intellectual property situations. TAL Global’s service concept is based on creating a group of strategic alliances, which affords our clients cost-effective and reliable resources to assess, plan and manage the full spectrum of services world-wide. Service levels are fully scalable to fit the particular needs of an organization; TAL Global professionals can provide both on-site and off-site operations. We understand the sensitive nature of many investigative and security issues, we operate with the utmost discretion and confidentiality in each and every situation. Our professionalism and complete transparency has earned us international recognition as a leader in the field of investigational services. Protecting people, assets and information is core to our comprehensive services offerings. We invite you to learn more about TAL Global.
